"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DiscontiguousSlice"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DiscontiguousSlice","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/DiscontiguousSlice","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A collection wrapper that provides access to the elements of a collection,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"indexed by a set of indices."}]},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift":{"type":"topic","title":"Swift","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Build apps using a powerful open language."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"/documentation/swift","role":"collection","identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift"},"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Sequence/Element":{"identifier":"doc://com.apple.Swift/documentation/Swift/Sequence/Element","url":"/documentation/swift/sequence/element","title":"Element","fragments":[{"text":"associatedtype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Element","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type representing the sequence’s elements."}],"required":true,"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"}}}